== Spelled as "大国霊神社" == This variant uses the character {{ill|霊|ja|霊|12=draft|12=draft}} (rei) instead of {{ill|魂|ja|魂|12=draft|12=draft}} (tama). The reading may be "Ōkunitama Jinja" or "Ōkunirei Jinja". * {{ill|Owari Ōkunitama Shrine|ja|尾張大国霊神社|12=draft|12=draft}} – located in {{ill|Aichi Prefecture|ja|愛知県|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Inazawa City|ja|稲沢市|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Kokufumiya Shrine|ja|国府宮 (稲沢市)|12=draft|12=draft}}: also known as Kokufumiya Shrine.
